\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces The Token Bomb attack: an adversarial prompt instructs the model to generate a long response containing a nested prompt that instructs the model to generate another long response. The recursive nesting causes context allocation to grow exponentially, exhausting GPU memory within seconds. The defense enforces a hard memory budget $M_{max}$ at the \textit  {Fact Layer}\ layer, rejecting any inference that would exceed the budget before the model processes the prompt.}}{2}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:token-bomb}{{1}{2}{The Token Bomb attack: an adversarial prompt instructs the model to generate a long response containing a nested prompt that instructs the model to generate another long response. The recursive nesting causes context allocation to grow exponentially, exhausting GPU memory within seconds. The defense enforces a hard memory budget $M_{max}$ at the \fact \ layer, rejecting any inference that would exceed the budget before the model processes the prompt}{figure.1}{}}
